http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Three-year-old-boy-tortured-by-parents/article13987724.ece

A three -year-old boy was reportedly tortured by parents at Patancheru in Medak district. According to sources, Manohar, three and half years, was tortured by parents M. Radha and Shivakumar for the past few days. The cries of the boy were heard by neighbours and they informed the same to the police. Childline director M.S. Chandra reached the house, rescued the boy with the help of police and got him admitted in the hospital for treatment on Thursday. The boy has been shifted to Mahima Ministries for safe custody. Patancheru police are investigating.